  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nIf Keycard was frozen in logged-in state and User tries to sign another tx, Status will freeze on the PIN screen. In this case, reopening is needed to continue using the app.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/129910068-666b4db6-7ef8-43f1-bb0d-d3eb2dead20c.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open Wallet\r\n2. Send transaction > Enter invalid PIN 3 times\r\n3. Tap `Dismiss`\r\n4. Enter valid PIN or tap `Cancel` and try to sign a new tx\r\n5. Reopen Status\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: 1.15\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\ncc @bitgamma \r\n\r\n",
